Package: scidb4gh
Type: Package
Title: GA4GH inspired R-API for SciDB
Version: 0.1
Date: 2017-04-20
Author: Kriti Sen Sharma
Maintainer: Kriti Sen Sharma <ksen@paradigm4.com>
Description: GA4GH inspired R-API for SciDB. Used to load (register), maintain (update, delete), and retrieve (search, get) data. Multiple data types are supported e.g. clinical data, gene, transcript, RNASeq, GXP by microarray, variant, fusion etc.
Depends:
    data.table,
    tidyr,
    dplyr,
    yaml,
    reshape2,
    Biobase,
    jsonlite,
    scidb
License: file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
Suggests: testthat,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
